name: NekoTheCat
description:
This is a Dreambooth model of Neko the shorthair tabby cat. This model was created to get her exact markings, but may be useful for anyone trying generate a similar tabby cat.

Recommended settings:

Samplers: DPM++ 2S a Karras, DPM adaptive, DPM++ 2S a, DPM2 a Karras, or DPM++ SDE Karras

CFG Scales: 8.5-11

Steps: 20-50

modelVersions.name: Nekov3
modelVersions.description:
-Switched base model to DreamShaper

-Trained with higher step count(3000 vs 2400)

-Neko now leans more towards realism, takes some prodding to get very stylized results (slightly overfit, adding "photography, photorealism" to the negatives help)
